# -*- mode: snippet -*-
# name: readme-cpp-documentation
# key: readme-cpp-documentation
# --
** Documentation

Generate documentation using following targets:
- ~-t docs~ :: Generate all documentation.
- ~-t apidocs~ :: Generate API documentation.
- ~-t publicapidocs~ :: Generate only public API documentation for developing against this software's public interface.
- ~-t privateapidocs~ :: Generate only private API documentation for developing this software itself.
- ~-t graphviz~ :: Generate dependency graphs.
- ~-t userdocs~ :: Generate user documentation.

Example:
#+BEGIN_SRC sh
\$ cmake --build /path/to/output/directory/ -t apidocs
#+END_SRC

Documentation will be stored in the ~output/docs~ subdirectory of the build path.

#+BEGIN_VERSE
*Note:*
[[https://doxygen.nl][Doxygen]] is required for API documentation.
[[https://graphviz.org][Graphviz]] is required for dependency graphs.
[[https://asciidoctor.org][Asciidoctor]] is required for user documentation.
#+END_VERSE

$0